    <summary>Where is Event #2?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">Creative Labs, 6180 Atlanta Hwy, Alpharetta, GA 30004. Same area as Event #1.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>Is everything really 100% Halal?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">Absolutely. All our meat is 100% Zabiha Halal. We are Muslim-owned and operated, and our kitchen maintains strict halal standards. No alcohol is used in any recipe or served at any event.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>What are birria tacos?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">Birria tacos are slow-braised meat stuffed into a crispy tortilla and served with a rich beef consomé for dipping. Choose chicken or beef filling &mdash; both come with our beef consomé. Scratch-made and 100% Zabiha Halal.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>What is chorizo?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">Chorizo is bold, juicy Mexican-seasoned ground beef packed with smoky spices and a little heat. It's not dry or hard &mdash; it's rich, crumbly, and loaded with flavor. Our Loaded Chorizo Fries are smothered in it with melted cheese on top.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>What is a Halal Michelada?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">A Michelada is a classic Mexican drink that's tangy, savory, and refreshing &mdash; usually made with beer. Ours is 100% halal and zero alcohol. Same bold flavor &mdash; lime, chili, spices &mdash; without compromising your values. Nobody else in Atlanta is doing this.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>What if I don't pre-pay?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">You can still come and pay at the door &mdash; but it's full price (22.99/44.99/74.99) and first come, first serve. If your flight sells out online, there's no guarantee at the door. The safest move is to pre-pay now.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>Is there seating?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">Limited tables on a first-come, first-served basis. Most guests enjoy the street-food experience &mdash; grab a table if one's open, or enjoy your flight from the car.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>What about weather?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">Outdoor event, so dress for the forecast. Atlanta evenings can get cool &mdash; bring a jacket so you can enjoy your flight comfortably.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>Are there restrooms on site?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">No permanent restrooms at this location. Plan accordingly before you arrive. The event is about 1–2 hours, so you'll be fine.</div>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>What if I can't make it?</summary>
    <div class="faq-answer">Pre-pay flights are non-refundable but fully transferable. Send a friend, or hold your credit toward Event #3. Text us at <a href="tel:1-678-208-8774" style="color: var(--green); font-weight: 600;">1-678-208-8774</a> before Feb 26.</div>
